title: Jay Lake - Endurance (Green Universe #2)
description:
Written by Jay Lake
Read by Katherine Kellgren
Format: MP3
Bitrate: 96 Kbps
Unabridged

Green is back in Copper Downs. Purchased from her father in sunny Selistan when she was four years old,
she was harshly raised to be a courtesan, companion, and bedmate of the Immortal Duke of Copper Downs.
But Green rebelled.Green killed the Duke, and many others, and won her freedom. Yet she is still claimed by
the gods and goddesses of her world, and they still require her service. Their demands are greater than any
duke's could have been.
